data.description:
Introducing this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom single family home built in 2006, this beautifully designed residence boasts a generous 2,081 square feet of living space, offering both comfort and style to its fortunate residents.

As you step through the front door, you'll immediately notice the inviting ambiance that defines this home. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal space for both everyday living and entertaining.

Featuring stunning granite countertops and warm wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances provide the tools needed to craft delicious meals, while the ample counter space ensures that every culinary creation is a breeze.

The spacious master bedroom is a sanctuary of comfort and relaxation. Step into the master suite, and you'll find a walk-in closet that effortlessly accommodates your wardrobe needs. The Roman tub in the master bathroom invites you to unwind after a long day, providing a spa-like retreat within your own home.

One of the standout features of this property is the seamless transition from indoor to outdoor living. French doors open up to reveal a screened patio that beckons you to step outside. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue with friends and family, this outdoor space is the perfect setting. Beyond the patio, a sparkling saltwater pool awaits, offering refreshing dips on warm Florida days.

This home also includes a convenient two-car garage, ensuring that your vehicles are both protected and easily accessible.

Enjoy access to pristine beaches, world-class golf courses, and a variety of dining and shopping options. The city's vibrant cultural scene and proximity to natural wonders like the St. Lucie River make it an ideal location for those seeking a balanced Florida lifestyle.

With its tasteful design, luxurious features, and ideal location, it offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your new home and experience the best of Florida living.
